{"tid":1781851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"番澳門或大陸千奇唔好用港豬澳大橋 要強制影相","createTime":"2019-12-13T12:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:29:47.000Z","uid":72149,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"86d269278d572c963a9b19590e9585f14c325e19","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"由12月開始到22號 澳門就泥回歸 <br />\n所以用港豬澳大橋去到一半 有個人工島要落車做安檢 check 果到的告示牌寫住（平時唔洗）<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題係 係個人工島上嘅安檢 要你影一張正面相 同埋比身分證、回鄉證佢 （好似平時過關咁）<br />\n<br />\n變相 即係你已經比人強制影左張相做人面辦識 <br />\n入左大陸數據到  係好恐怖一件事<br />\n所以 大家千奇要小心 迫住要番大陸 澳門都唔好用港豬澳大橋  <br />\n我朋友搭船就冇事<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"e89a31b5b9d647467fd4d148dc00fb176d4f6e8a","tid":1781851,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"(重開) 發動世界級遊行！#Who stands with us世界巡遊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"173980ec8be2bc4dd7261a68bba9e9e99ab091d8","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5caae22f56d3517c4e0738c685b79a1244a4531","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6940773b622e8a6d685a988d66222508f78759f","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"推比手足睇"},{"pid":"a3cb55ac93b6ef3e85ea0b42afdbffd6c64f2d5e","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5b47651d60a1652c850401a74d63f4da3a15241","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"765d5f4ec5c99297c02c1b6ab1b4c03f63dd4e0b","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2416acc0544ffd018ef2950066f13eac420407a6","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfdfcc528c5ab8ce9be70bc82a51aa9b2f42eead","tid":1781851,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"澳門已經=大陸<br />\n永遠唔好去啦   除非有好重要事"},{"pid":"e4aa375026634b5c181c549999d86fdc7b579f0a","tid":1781851,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"好彩未用過"},{"pid":"20fcc55d69a03101508f08ebdfc5c7678d7ebcb5","tid":1781851,"uid":179114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"過澳門要帶回鄉證咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430d94557ba9127b6ed1cf9021e46568fca27a1b","tid":1781851,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"澳門=大陸， 根本唔應該再去"},{"pid":"c208c619ea3412083619df40485df2b570e1861b","tid":1781851,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"港珠澳橋：大陸<br />\nturbojet : 何超瓊<br />\n金光飛航： 珠江客運<br />\n<br />\n做人做狗自己諗"},{"pid":"b5e28592537e3fcd377b73ec17ee78d8852638b8","tid":1781851,"uid":15512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"尋晚要去澳門做野<br />\n氹仔一落船已經有差佬好似鎖定左目標咁<br />\n叫我去搜袋check電話,部電話仲有啲文宣相係到<br />\n跟住佢影低我部電話啲野<br />\n唔sure影咩,應該係文宣相<br />\n親眼睇到佢影低左部電話既IMEI<br />\n跟住搞左一粒鐘左右就比張野我話拒絕入境<br />\n原因係懷疑我會影響澳門安全,即刻搭下班船走<br />\n由落船到搜袋check電話全程有cam錄住<br />\n個人覺得由上船開始就有澳門差佬鎖定哂目標<br />\n因為見住有個人一落船就拎部電話影低我個樣<br />\n所以要去澳門既巴絲小心啲<br />\n利申: 六月到而家都冇比狗逗過"},{"pid":"6ddb6ee3f4dfaa2025e29f0c5d9da45e7d07a636","tid":1781851,"uid":72149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"我岩岩入到澳門 又比人抽樣檢查 佢地帶我入一間房 咩都冇  得張枱同埋椅  幾個人圍住我要搜我袋  審犯咁審"},{"pid":"fac11fbdf0c689c8b769a4c54b98a1887d4d5976","tid":1781851,"uid":53780,"li